ton\" href=\"javascript: history.go(-1)\"><i class=\"fa fa-arrow-left\"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Go Back</a></div>\n\n          <br /><br /><br />\n\n          <div class=\"col-md-7 col-sm-7\">\n            <h1>Your collection details</h1>\n\t\t\t\n            \n            <div class=\"collect\">\n              <p class=\"address-line\">\n                                THE MOUNT,                 47,                 FLAT 3,                 GRANGE ROAD,                 LEWES,                 LEWES,                 EAST SUSSEX,                 BN7 1TT              </p>\n\n                              <p>We collect your rubbish on: <strong>Mondays</strong></p>\n                <p>Your next rubbish collection day is: <strong>29th December 2025</strong></p>\n              \n                              <p>We collect your recycling on: <strong>Tuesdays</strong></p>\n                <p>Your next recycling collection day is: <strong>6th January 2026</strong></p>\n              \n              \n            </div>\n            <div class=\"block\">\n\n                  <h2>Download your collection calendar:</h2>\n  <p><a href=\"https://www.lewes-eastbourne.gov.uk/article/1627/Christmas-and-New-Year-bin-collections-and-tree-recycling\">Quick reference guide to changes over Christmas and bank holidays</a>.</p>\n \n\t\t\t\t      <a class=\"button\" href=\"downloads/Lewes/CV40.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fa fa-download\"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Download Refuse and Recycling (PDF)</a>\n        <a class=\"button\" href=\"downloads/Lewes/CV40.ics\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"fa fa-download\"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Download Refuse and Recycling (ICS)</a>\n      <p>ICS files can be added to your digital calendar like Outlook, Google Calendar and similar.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-5\">\n  <div id=\"check-collection\">\n<h3>When is your collection day?</h3>\n\n\t<div class=\"search-form\">\n\t\n\t<form name=\"search\" id=\"search\" action=\"results.php\" method=\"post\">\n    <fieldset>\n    \n\t<input type=\"text\" id=\"property_no\" name=\"property_no\" placeholder=\"House name or number\" >\n\t<input type=\"hidden\" value=\"\" id=\"property_name\" name=\"property_name\" placeholder=\"Enter your House/Flat Name\" >\n\t<input type=\"hidden\" value=\"\" id=\"street\" name=\"street\" placeholder=\"Enter your Street\" >\n\t<input type=\"text\" id=\"postcode\" name=\"postcode\" required placeholder=\"Your postcode\" >\n        \n\t<button type=\"submit\" id=\"searchbtn\"><i class=\"fa fa-search\"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Show me my days!</button>\n\t</fieldset>\n\t</form>\n    \n    </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!--<div class=\"gw-warning\">\n    <p>Please note: There are no refuse, recycling or garden waste collections on Wednesday 25 December, Thursday 26 December or Wednesday 1 January.</p>\n</div>--></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- -->\n\n</div>\n\n\n        <div class=\"fluid-container video\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n        \n            <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n                <h1>Find out about Recycling Around the Home</h1>\n                <div class=\"videoWrapper\">\n                <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/sLktjtlXCNo?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n        </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"fluid-container why\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n        \n            <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n                <div class=\"col-md-4 col-sm-12 locator\">\n                    <!-- <script src=\"https://rl.recyclenow.com/wrap-rlw.js\" async></script> -->\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-md-7 col-sm-12 col-md-offset-1\">\n                <!-- <img src=\"images/7363_Recycle_card_and_paper_web_banner_2.0.gif\" width=\"515\"> -->\n                <h2>Why recycle?</h2>\n                <p>Ten years ago, the UK recycled less than 5% of waste from around the home. Today, around 40% of our household waste is recycled in East Sussex, but we could recycle more. Recycling more from around the home helps save money that can be spent on other essential Council services. If every household in East Sussex recycled one more shampoo bottle we would save enough energy to power a typical primary school for 37 days.</p>\n                </div>   \n            </div>\n            \n        </div>\n        </div>\n<div class=\"push\"></div>\n\n</section>\n\n<footer class=\"fluid-container\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <img class=\"recycle\" src=\"images/recycle.svg\" width=\"130\" height=\"43\">\n    <img class=\"love\" src=\"images/love.svg\" width=\"116\" height=\"70\">\n  </div>\n</footer>\n\n      \n\n    <!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap's JavaScript plugins) -->\n    <script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n    <!-- Include all compiled plugins (below), or include individual files as needed -->\n    <script src=\"js/bootstrap.min.js\"></script>\n\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/validate/jquery.validate.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/jquery.placeholder.js\"></script>\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/functions.js\"></script>\n\n\n\n  </body>\n</html>\n",
